{"type":"message","id":"90fc4cee","parentId":"d90bb5a4","timestamp":"2026-04-07T04:33:13.867Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-ac298c22e975153c","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-06.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 25,\n      \"score\": 0.6549620082946855,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-04-06 — Monday\\n\\n## Events\\n- Morning: Sent \\\"Word of the Day: Meraki\\\" to Nrexya group\\n- Nemesis replied \\\"Nice word\\\" — appreciated the word choice\\n- Heartbeat health monitor cron ran at 5:00 PM UTC\\n\\n## People\\n- Nemesis: likes the word \\\"meraki\\\"\\n\\n## Decisions\\n- None\\n\\n## Lessons\\n- None\\n\\n## Infrastructure\\n- None\\n\\n## Pending\\n- None\\n\\n## Tomorrow\\n- None\\n\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 24,\n      \"endLine\": 41,\n      \"score\": 0.5856062151275355,\n      \"snippet\": \"- **Memory:** Gemini embeddings + BM25 hybrid with temporal decay; can search conversation transcripts\\n- **GitHub:** Backup at https://github.com/tempint001-cpu/openclaw-workspace — auto-push every 2h via cron\\n- **TTS:** functional via `tts` tool\\n- **Group:** Nrexya (-1003606834639); respond only when @mentioned\\n- **Heartbeat:** every 30 min, 7 AM–11 PM IST; 6 tasks + state persistence\\n- **Heartbeat State:** `memory/heartbeat-state.json` — tracks last runs for continuity (skill: heartbeat-state-manager)\\n- **Backup Verifier:** `scripts/backup_verifier.py` — verifies memory files are committed and pushed\\n- **Cron jobs (11):** good-morning (DM), ai-news-digest, good-morning (group), word-of-the\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-03.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 20,\n      \"score\": 0.5564078207490216,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-04-03 — Friday\\n\\n## Log\\n- Goodnight story sent to N